Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:25.78,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:28.33,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}世间万物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.70,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my power,future
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:32.16,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}于此始动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:33.46,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.96,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}伴君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:38.34,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my power,future
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:48.05,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}若要唤出情感之名 则无休无止无穷无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:56.10,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}你的眼神传来呼唤 我以本能即可分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.98,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}相伴相随
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.23,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}不离不弃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:02.82,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}无论光明抑或黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:06.66,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}如紧凑相连的拼图零片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:10.95,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}一切皆有其因果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:15.17,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}萍水相逢也好 命中注定也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:19.84,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}终将指引我们走向所坚信的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:26.64,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}赤诚真心 逐步升温
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:30.47,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}无虚情假意 非利益所趋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:35.19,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}以真实自我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:38.98,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}立于所盼之地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:42.65,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}愿君侧耳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:44.03,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my reason
